== Tweakr ==

TUMBLR

	Current features:

		* Edit the size of the tumblr editor
		* Adds "quicktags" for consistent tagging
		* Adds buttons to the WYSIWYG for adding code snippets to your text blogs

	Future features:

		* An "embed" button to quickly inject vimeo / youtube / etc HTML snippets
		* Possibly a complete replacement of the editor

FACEBOOK, GITHUB, TUMBLR, TWITTER, GOOGLE DOCS

	Future features:

		* Add notifications to the favicon